OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771876127
OL,3,CSouthern drivers rated 'worst' in
OL,4,CEngland as bad behaviour puts lives at
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FWatch: National Highways has released
OL,8,Fvideo of poor driving on the motorway
OL,9,Fnetwork, including tailgating and
OL,10,Fmiddle lane hogging.
OL,12,FDrivers in Southern England have been
OL,13,Frated as the worst in the country,
OL,14,Ffollowing new research by National
OL,15,FHighways.
OL,17,FMany motorists in London, the South,
OL,18,Fand South East are lacking basic road
OL,19,Fmanners, with 41% admitting to
OL,20,Ftailgating others whilst out on the
OL,21,Froads.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
