OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771876127
OL,3,CSouthern drivers rated 'worst' in
OL,4,CEngland as bad behaviour puts lives at
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,FTailgating contributes to around 8% of
OL,8,Fpeople killed or seriously injured
OL,9,Feach year on motorways and major A-
OL,10,Froads, based on long term Department
OL,11,Ffor Transport data.
OL,13,FDr Neale Kinnear, a behavioural
OL,14,Fpsychologist specialising in driving
OL,15,Fbehaviours, said: "Most of us see
OL,16,Fourselves as considerate people, but
OL,17,Fdriving is a unique context.
OL,26,@wD@SOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,418,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1771876127
OL,3,CSouthern drivers rated 'worst' in
OL,4,CEngland as bad behaviour puts lives at
OL,5,Crisk
OL,7,F"It's goal focused and often time
OL,8,Fpressured. When we're running late or
OL,9,Fbehind other traffic, frustration can
OL,10,Fbuild. In that moment, closing the gap
OL,11,Fcan feel like taking control or making
OL,12,Fprogress.
OL,14,F"The reality is different. Drivers
OL,15,Ftend to overestimate how much time, if
OL,16,Fany, they save by pushing on. As
OL,17,Ffrustration rises, perspective on the
OL,18,Fimportance of keeping a safe margin,
OL,19,Fand the impact it has on others can be
OL,20,Flost."
OL,26,@vD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
